      { "key": "message", "label": "Your Message", "type": "textarea", "default": "I came across your venue and it clearly has real atmosphere — the kind of place people remember. I build premium, conversion-focused websites for restaurants, barbers and hospitality brands: custom-coded, mobile-first, and designed to look as good as your space feels.", "placeholder": "I came across your venue..." },
      { "key": "message2", "label": "Second Paragraph", "type": "textarea", "default": "Everything's built with the floor, the chair and the front door in mind — reservations, online ordering and local SEO baked in from day one. I'd love to put together a free live mockup so you can feel the flow before deciding anything.", "placeholder": "A second paragraph to add depth..." },
